description: The House of Falafel is a food truck created by a restaurant of the same name, serving the DC streets with Tunisian Mediterranean cuisine - a blend of Mediterranean and desert dwellers' culinary traditions. Its distinctive use of spices comes from the many civilizations which have ruled the land now known as Tunisia; Phoenicians, Romans, Arabs, and Turks. Each tradition lends its own distinct flavor, bringing a delicious new combination to your mouth.
name: The House of Falafel
